00:47:39,699 --> 00:47:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] Prirodno je da kao roditelji osjećamo strah.

807
00:47:42,179 --> 00:47:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] Prirodno je da ne znamo.

808
00:47:44,300 --> 00:47:46,840
[SPEAKER_01] Prirodno je da kao osoba koja nikad ne koristi,

809
00:47:46,840 --> 00:47:48,360
[SPEAKER_01] mreže da gleda šta je sad to,

810
00:47:48,360 --> 00:47:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] zašto sad oni to rade,

811
00:47:49,460 --> 00:47:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] zašto tako kratki vide.

812
00:47:51,239 --> 00:47:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ali idemo se o tom informirati.

813
00:47:52,980 --> 00:47:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo zauzeti stav, ono, a priori,

814
00:47:55,440 --> 00:47:56,739
