1307
01:18:28,020 --> 01:18:30,060
[SPEAKER_01] A to nije jedna mjera

1308
01:18:30,060 --> 01:18:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] kojom će te riješiti problem.

1309
01:18:31,840 --> 01:18:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je dugotrajan proces.

1310
01:18:33,539 --> 01:18:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je čak i strateški proces

1311
