1330
01:19:07,979 --> 01:19:12,399
[SPEAKER_00] I evo da zaključimo ovu temu.

1331
01:19:12,399 --> 01:19:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] Postoje li neki

1332
01:19:14,279 --> 01:19:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] efikasni načini

1333
