[SPEAKER_00] otkrijemo ljepotu jezika

1335
01:19:20,600 --> 01:19:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] i pisma

1336
01:19:21,680 --> 01:19:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili zapravo s razvojem

1337
01:19:23,699 --> 01:19:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] interneta i društvenih mreža

1338
01:19:25,880 --> 01:19:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] nekako nema povratka

1339
01:19:27,619 --> 01:19:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] na one stare?

1340
01:19:29,659 --> 01:19:31,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tu optimist.

1341
01:19:31,859 --> 01:19:33,779
[SPEAKER_01] Gledajući primjere

1342
01:19:33,779 --> 01:19:35,399
[SPEAKER_01] nekih mojih prijatelja

1343
