01:22:50,380 --> 01:22:52,199
[SPEAKER_01] To kako vrijeme prolazi,

1472
01:22:52,199 --> 01:22:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] kasnije shvatite

1473
01:22:53,359 --> 01:22:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] što ste sve propustili.

1474
01:22:54,500 --> 01:22:55,939
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo je uložite

1475
01:22:55,939 --> 01:22:57,479
[SPEAKER_01] jako puno u svoju edukaciju.

1476
01:22:57,479 --> 01:22:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] Nijedan trenutak

1477
01:22:59,260 --> 01:23:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] neće biti izgubljen.

1478
01:23:00,319 --> 01:23:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ukradite malo vremena

1479
01:23:02,260 --> 01:23:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] od tih trenutaka

1480
01:23:03,659 --> 01:23:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] opuštanja u kojima nas ponesu

1481
01:23:06,359 --> 01:23:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] sve, cijeli taj svijet

1482
01:23:07,680 --> 01:23:08,939
[SPEAKER_01] o kojem smo da nas govorili.

1483
01:23:08,939 --> 01:23:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] Izborite ga više baš za sebe.

1484
01:23:11,340 --> 01:23:13,180
[SPEAKER_01] Baš za to zona

1485
01:23:13,180 --> 01:23:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj ću biti samo ja

1486
01:23:15,039 --> 01:23:16,819
