1503
01:23:46,819 --> 01:23:49,319
[SPEAKER_01] I mislim da sve to skupa

1504
01:23:49,319 --> 01:23:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] stvara onda jedno okružje

1505
01:23:51,119 --> 01:23:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] u kojemu ćemo zaista se moći zboriti

1506
01:23:54,260 --> 01:23:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] za bolje perspektive.

1507
01:23:55,460 --> 01:23:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da stvarno

1508
