1510
01:24:00,279 --> 01:24:01,979
[SPEAKER_01] onima kojima je naša pomoć potrebna.

1511
01:24:01,979 --> 01:24:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo mi sami sebi dostatni.

1512
01:24:03,960 --> 01:24:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] To je jako važno prepoznat

1513
01:24:05,800 --> 01:24:07,380
