1515
01:24:10,060 --> 01:24:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] i uvijek volim pohvaliti

1516
01:24:12,119 --> 01:24:13,140
[SPEAKER_01] one koji volontira.

1517
01:24:13,140 --> 01:24:14,819
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, to mi je...

1518
01:24:14,819 --> 01:24:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kad mogu birat u smislu suradnika

1519
01:24:17,260 --> 01:24:18,760
[SPEAKER_01] koji su volonteri

1520
01:24:18,760 --> 01:24:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] i koji su isključivo fokusirani na posao,

1521
01:24:20,920 --> 01:24:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek biram volontere.

1522
01:24:22,380 --> 01:24:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] Oni s kojima se družim,

1523
01:24:24,260 --> 01:24:25,380
